    <h1 class="content_title">Venue</h1>
  </div>

  The 2016 summit will be held at the <b>MIT Sloan Building (E52) in the Samberg
  Conference Cente</b>, 50 Memorial Drive, Cambridge, MA 02142 USA. The venue is
  <b>public transit accessible</b> and located within a 5-minute walk of the
  Kendall/MIT station on the MBTA Red Line.<br><br>

  <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=zj8jm2uSOoZ8.kwsCB5wZs_bI"
  width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0;"></iframe> <br><br>

  <b>Public transportation directions</b><br>
  We recommend taking public transportation to the Summit to reduce our environmental footprint. MIT Building E52 is located within a 5-minute walk from the Kendall/MIT stop on the Red Line. For more information about public transportation in the Boston area please visit the <a href="http://www.mbta.com/">MBTA</a> website.<br>
  <ol>
      <li>Take the Red Line to the Kendall/MIT stop.</li>
      <li>Walk straight up Main Street toward Longfellow Bridge.</li>
      <li>Make a right onto Wadsworth St. (at the corner with Bank of America).</li>
      <li>Building E52 at MIT is located at the intersection of Wadsworth St. and Memorial Dr.</li>
  </ol><br>

  <a href="http://web.mit.edu/mitdlbc/www/parking.htm">Parking Directions</a><br><br>

